                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable C</hi> 180.) I was sent for—I found on the prisoner fifteen pieces marked in hit right-hand waistcoat pocket—the prosecutor said he knew them.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
